\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 How did your mother and father expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Well we had to do as we were told. But - we never got thrashed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Did you always have to be very respectful?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Yes. That's one thing me mother did - teach me. We had to respect all our elders. Anyone, didn't matter who
 came to the house we had to get up and give our seats or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Did your mother bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Just help one }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 another\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 , that was all, all had to help one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Suppose there was fighting broke out what were you supposed to do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Well - she used to - come - she would stop it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Suppose you were away from your mother and one of your brothers bit you -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 What would she expect you to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Well she didn't say to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 What would you think she would expect you to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 
Well I don't know what - what me mother would say but I can tell you one incident me father. I tell you I used to go - go down and get these sovereigns in me bag and after me mother died - when we moved to South Shields }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 back}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 
, to me grandmother see. I still used to go for these sovereigns. And we used to have come over the South Shields ferry, it's still run yet, and every Friday night a got a hiding.
