\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 No. There was a g
ang of lads there. There was a gang - they used to wait for me every Friday night. They never took any money from me or anything. But buy God they used to give me a hiding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 What for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Nothing. I didn't even know them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Was this when you had the money with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 They didn't know I had any money. No, they didn't know I had any money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 But you had it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Oh I had the money on us - in this little bag, leather bag it was round me neck. And every Friday night I used to get a hiding. Smas
h me collar. Used to always - they were celluloid collars you know and used to smash me collar. And there was one Friday night me father had gone to - he's not going to work you know. He says what's this I hear about you getting - a hiding? They follow yo
u
 every night when you come home? Oh, I said, I don't know, I says, them lads always set on us. Well, he said, look he says, when they set on you tonight, he says, set on them. He says, because if you don't, he says, I'm going to set on you. And I went hom
e and I can tell you I was scared stiff. When I got to that ferry and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 sure}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 
 enough the lads is waiting. And I - I thought to myself, well - I'm going to get a hiding anyway, see, because if I didn't get it - I didn't stand me ground with 'em I was going to g
et a hiding off me father. So - I did, I stood me ground. And by God I give them a hiding. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 And unknown to me - me father had been watching us. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
