\insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 , I says, because you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 canna}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884  take these off us. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped that you and your brothers and sisters would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Eeh - I don't know because me mother - she had such a life she hardly knew - me father didn't care a damn. I couldn't answer that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Except that he didn't want you pushed around did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Oh yes wanted - you had to stick up for yourself. In fact, he wouldn't let anybody put upon one. When he was with you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Can you think of any things your mother or father thought were very important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Well I - I can tell you one instance of me
 father. There was one night I was sent to look for him and he happened to be on a day shift this week and - I went down to the pub where he would be in, round at Castle, the corner pub, I can remember - and I - going into the bar, of course youngsters co
u
ld go in the bar in these days, and - his mate, well he was his labourer actually, called him Dick Sirey, he called to me, he said, come on, he says, out here, he says, he says, there'd going to be trouble in here. I said, what - if there's going to be tr
ouble - I want me dad out. So - I said, I'm not going 'til me dad comes out, I said, me - me grandmas sent us, said and if I go home without him, I says, I'll get one. So seeing this - bigger - this was in South }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
