 w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 ould}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884  steal everybody's beer.
