nd he - he drinks the pint. Me father just walks across and hits him. Did I tell you what I do }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8330246\charrsid8601884 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884  they}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
