\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 What happened if you did something your parents disapproved of?
