\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 Well - when I first started as a casual we had no guarantee or anything. You just used to come i
n and get what work there was going. But it was like everything else, the boss had his favourites. And - of course I was in the South }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3558474\charrsid8601884 Shields}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884  then. And I've seen me walk three nights a week from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3558474\charrsid8601884 J}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13321278\charrsid8601884 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3558474\charrsid8601884 sm}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13321278\charrsid8601884 ond}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884  to South Shields you know, three nights a week. Walk 
