\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12721239 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 That's not so good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13512717 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884 No, 
it was a hard life. Well, such as Howes, the funeral people, Bargesons, they used to ring in see if there's any spare drivers available. Then you used to go down and do funeral work or something like that.
