he was the area engineer, well, have you enjoyed it? I said, yes, very interesting. He said, do you think you'll manage? Oh, I said, I've no doubt I'll manage but, I says, I've still got a lot to learn yet. I says, don't think I've learnt everything in tw
o
 weeks. I says, only way I'm going to learn is the practical work. I says, I have done the practical work while I've been down there, assembling them and pulling them to bits and assembling them again you know and - they give you a box with a machine in, 
