ow see what you can do with that, put it together, such as that thing. But, I said, I've no doubt that I'll manage all right. Well, he says, you've got a - a job on your own here. I says, I'll take you down now to your workshop, a lovely workshop, down Ga
l
leygate there. He says, you're the boss in here. You can even order me out look, he says, I'm your boss, but, he says, if you don't want me in this room, he says, you have authority to order me out. He says, you've taken a very responsible position, he sa
y
s, it doesn't matter who comes, inspectors, anybody, he says, if you don't want them in you order them out. No doubt, he says, they will be coming in for - to learn about these machines, you know, on the road and that. Well, I says, there's nothing they'r
