e machines. I said, that's right, I says, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3558474\charrsid8601884 there\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1460185\charrsid8601884  nobody can twist the machines. They're supposed to be }{\rtlch\fcs1 
